ttp_template:
<group name="list_name_seq_action_network">
ip prefix-list {{LIST_NAME}} seq {{SEQ}} {{ACTION}} {{NETWORK | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="list_name_seq_action_network_le">
ip prefix-list {{LIST_NAME}} seq {{SEQ}} {{ACTION}} {{NETWORK}} le {{LE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="list_name_seq_action_network_ge_le">
ip prefix-list {{LIST_NAME}} seq {{SEQ}} {{ACTION}} {{NETWORK}} ge {{GE}} le {{LE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
ip prefix-list TEST seq 5 permit 10.0.0.0/8
ip prefix-list TEST seq 10 permit 172.16.0.0/12 le 24
ip prefix-list TEST seq 15 permit 192.168.1.0/24 ge 25 le 28
ip prefix-list TEST seq 20 deny 192.168.10.0/24
textfsm_template:
Value LIST_NAME (\S+)
Value SEQ (\d+)
Value ACTION (permit|deny)
Value NETWORK (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+\/\d+)
Value GE (\d+)
Value LE (\d+)

Start
  ^ip\s+prefix-list\s+${LIST_NAME}\s+seq\s+${SEQ}\s+${ACTION}\s+${NETWORK}\s+ge\s+${GE}\s+le\s+${LE}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^ip\s+prefix-list\s+${LIST_NAME}\s+seq\s+${SEQ}\s+${ACTION}\s+${NETWORK}\s+le\s+${LE}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^ip\s+prefix-list\s+${LIST_NAME}\s+seq\s+${SEQ}\s+${ACTION}\s+${NETWORK}\s*$$ -> Record
